&quot;This Is War&quot; is a song by American rock band 30 Seconds to Mars, featured on their third studio album This Is War. Written by lead vocalist Jared Leto, the song was released as the second single from the album to American radio on March 8, 2010, and the physical single was released on March 26, 2010.

 Leto told MTV News (Source <a href="http://www.songfacts.com/detail.php?id=17896" rel="nofollow">This Is War Songfacts</a>): &quot;The song is really about conflict, and the album really is about it too: the inevitability of conflict, the blessing of conflict and what we can all learn from it.&quot;

 It is also available as DLC for the popular Rhythm Game &quot;Rock Band&quot;

